text: Choi Soo-yeon (Hangul: 최수연, born 23 November 1990) is a South Korean sabre fencer. She participated at the 2019 World Fencing Championships, winning a bronze medal in the team competition. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean sabre fencers Category:South Korean female fencers Category:Fencers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games gold medalists for South Korea Category:Asian Games medalists in fencing Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games
